    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《忆蚀》Subliminal是一款受到都市传说“后室”启发的第一人称解谜游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公发现自己被困在了记忆中，来到一个充满超现实和后室风格的建筑内。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然，这里有他童年的回忆，但随着剧情的展开，记忆被逐渐侵蚀，环境产生扭曲和变形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他需独自克服黑暗和恐惧，挑战各种谜题和实体生物......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/b11774f34ec42cbfcd91beb89e2a6d4b.avif?t=1770509141\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       使用UE5引擎开发，拥有尖端的光影和渲染技术，画面逼真细腻，光影效果极其出色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       游戏中玩家发现自己被困在由记忆构成的后室风格建筑中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       如同梦境般重回了似曾相识，但又违反逻辑的超现实场景。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/e25635b33b65679d1e89e0ee95f695d3.poster.avif?t=1770509141\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/e25635b33b65679d1e89e0ee95f695d3.webm?t=1770509141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/e25635b33b65679d1e89e0ee95f695d3.mp4?t=1770509141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/7f2d15ece78c7e078ab35321a0654bb8.avif?t=1770509141\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       首发版本会推出多个风格迥异的游戏关卡，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       沉闷压抑的地下室，悄然无声的水上世界，错综复杂的儿童乐园...... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       每个关卡都会有若干挑战，通过后可进入不同的关卡，并最终影响游戏结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/caa8351bf5f63caa891f76acdc54524a.poster.avif?t=1770509141\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/caa8351bf5f63caa891f76acdc54524a.webm?t=1770509141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/caa8351bf5f63caa891f76acdc54524a.mp4?t=1770509141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/f9538a1ee7db95e991d2a60d177df757.avif?t=1770509141\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       游戏的各个关卡中设计了丰富的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       操控光线，考验观察，逻辑思维，想象力，甚至考验操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       玩家也会遭遇并面对各种实体和生物，每种都呈现独特的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       每种挑战都充满乐趣，并且会触发不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/83a4804e0f9fd04fa58d81ffffd148af.poster.avif?t=1770509141\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/83a4804e0f9fd04fa58d81ffffd148af.webm?t=1770509141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/83a4804e0f9fd04fa58d81ffffd148af.mp4?t=1770509141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/45843172aa3acc058b0f7f2432187485.avif?t=1770509141\" width=600 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       游戏中每一个场景，虽然都似曾相识，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       但通过空间，光影和声音的设计运用，营造出压抑和诡异的氛围，令人心悸和焦虑不安。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       尤其是当记忆出现侵蚀，画面变得扭曲和变形，甚至出现实体生物......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300840/extras/Gameplay_gif04.gif?t=1770509141\" /></span></p>",
